{
  "stem": "18186.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until they actually came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But up to then, I didn't-- I didn't-- I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, they-- when they-- when they came in-- before they came in, the Russian came into our town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1913-- in 1939 the Russian came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stayed in our-- in my area for-- and up until the German came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, like-- it was, like, a year or maybe a year and a half, we were-- well, the Russian-- and then the German came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- Let's talk about the Russian occupation a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You say they stayed in Stepan?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russians were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian were-- they were the Russian government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, what happened-- what I did to my life, [LAUGHS] I switched from public school to-- to-- to-- to a Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, it was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were learning in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we were learning Russian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I could have gone to the public school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all in Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was changed from Polish to Russian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I felt as the Jewish person, I felt I wanted to be in the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't do that before because we could not afford it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So because-- but they also learned-- we also-- it was only, not only Jewish that was allowed, we went-- we learned Russian, we were learned Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This book-- I-- we learned a few languages that we will-- we knew, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was not just like here, English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was more than one language--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think all my friends switched, so I switched.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they was-- they were running-- that was the government.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
